title: Dwayne ‘The Rock’ Johnson Manifests Kids for Travis Kelce: ‘We’re Putting That Voodoo Onto You & Taylor’
summary: The actor appeared on the tight end's New Heights podcast with Jason Kelce.
body: Taylor Swift and Travis Kelce might be on their way to starting a family, and Dwayne “The Rock” Johnson is ready for it. This device is a high-capacity power bank and a global mobile hotspot in one sleek unit. It’s designed to keep your gadgets fully charged and seamlessly connected, regardless of what corner of the globe you happen to be in.
